SBC Book Review App Config Notes:

Docker Info:

docker run -d \
  --name mariadb \
  -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=root \
  -e MYSQL_DATABASE=sbcreviews \
  -e MYSQL_USER=sbcuser \
  -e MYSQL_PASSWORD=sbcuser \
  -p 3306:3306 \
  mariadb:10.11

  verify user:
  docker exec -it mariadb mysql -u sbcuser -psbcuser sbcreviews

  Clear out broken containers, images, volumes and networks:
  Note: Be careful.  This deletes all stopped containers, dangling images, networks and volumes not used by a container.
  docker system prune -a --volumes -f

  List containers:
  docker ps -a

  Remove a container:
  docker rm -f b1ebab3b2f66_


  Rebuild everything from sratch:
  Note: -DskipTests build/packages project w/o running tests.  This may help to prevent errors when running the docker-compose build command.
    ./mvnw clean package -DskipTests
    docker-compose build --no-cache
    docker-compose up
